comments: Jackson Jr. (MEM) contests LeVert's (CLE) jump shot and the contact after the release, and follow-through, is marginal.
Wade (CLE) moves alongside Jackson Jr. (MEM) during his drive to the basket and marginal body contact occurs during his driving shot attempt.
Strus (CLE) establishes himself in a screening position in Williams Jr.'s (MEM) path and although he slightly extends his arms, the contact is marginal.
LeVert (CLE) is the last player to touch the ball before it goes out of bounds.
Jackson Jr. (MEM) establishes himself in Strus's (CLE) path and does not deliver illegal contact.  Jackson Jr. moves backwards after the contact with Strus occurs.
LeVert (CLE) plants his foot forwards after Williams Jr. (MEM) releases the pass and incidental foot contact occurs.
Jackson (MEM) gathers the ball on his left foot and hops consecutively on it.
Strus (CLE) moves laterally towards Jackson (MEM) and the resulting contact during his drive to the basket is marginal.
Williams Jr. (MEM) pushes Strus (CLE) to the floor and is assessed a flagrant foul, penalty 1.
Jackson (MEM) is the last player to touch the ball before it goes out of bounds.
Konchar (MEM) commits a take foul on Mitchell (CLE).
